          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "PREP"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "1b545aa4-27ea-4407-9856-71a369fb70a7",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "1. Label your freezer bag."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "baf23f85-4454-4113-a829-8111f2b54827",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "2. To your gallon-sized freezer bag, add all ingredients (except evaporated milk and"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "e75e4c59-973d-4f2e-9410-e9815670eb12",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "chicken broth). To keep potatoes from browning, chop them last and add the to the"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "48a63b1b-fecf-4d64-b284-e0c6478b0f08",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "top of your freezer bag."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "9c860c8e-ea82-4bd4-9588-f8c66a52277a",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "3. Add evaporated milk to a quart-sized plastic freezer bag. Seal, and add to gallonsized bag."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "bcb0d47b-9ef7-434c-b7fb-4271df457555",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "4. Remove as much air from the gallon-sized freezer bag as possible, seal, and lay flat"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "c3007adb-d681-4ae4-9fa2-2cf4906443a6",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "in your freezer."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "52578d0a-7112-449b-b82b-98034cfdcebd",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "COOK"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "39afc8ce-ade1-4202-9d04-717ed9f67169",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "1. The night before cooking, move frozen bag to your refrigerator to thaw."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "89004be5-b921-4627-a799-b4e55c002c19",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "2. The morning of cooking, pour contents of gallon-sized freezer bag into your"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "95ad8484-3fce-406e-a7df-73b88540c9e6",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "crockpot and add chicken broth. Keep bag of evaporated milk in the refrigerator."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "94c5ad11-aa2e-4625-b420-3e16192d19d7",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "3. Cook item in crockpot on \u201clow\u201d setting for 8 hours, or until carrots and potatoes"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "88c82775-b8f5-4d04-879f-8cd3d2fb839c",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "are soft. Stir in evaporated milk and leave lid open a crack. Continue to cook 15"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "05f3ce02-28b9-4b49-ab86-dd125595bb48",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "minutes or until heated through."
        }
      ],
